            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Rather than take the situation lying down, Toyota found a way to bring all its production lines back to normal levels by the beginning of December. While the auto giant is remaining tight-lipped about how it’s procuring the chips to pull that off, the company’s resilience is admirable. Read more about it ",
