            "text": "Eager to get on the good side of politicians, publications, and others who have criticized it for pushing against the “green” movement in the auto industry, Dodge excitedly announced its upcoming all-electric muscle car, or eMuscle car, back in July. While the people who were supposed to be impressed by the odd presentation applauded the move, we knew something wasn’t right.",
