          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Bucking the doomsday predictions, Harley-Davidson posted big sales and nice profits this year. To see an American icon do well when so many are dogging it is truly inspirational. Check out the story we ran about Harley’s Q2 sales results ",
