        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When the launch was finally revealed, Dodge added some additional security updates and has been using a confusing rollout schedule. It’s a lot to explain, so check out our breakdown of the announcement by Dodge ",
