          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It gets even worse: the cancelled 6th-gen Camaro Z/28 was going to use the same engine as the C8 Corvette Z06. Read more about this crazy story ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
